3
00:01:58,318 --> 00:02:00,487
(groaning)

4
00:02:09,996 --> 00:02:10,797
- Are you kidding me?

5
00:02:19,539 --> 00:02:20,373
Tim!

6
00:02:29,649 --> 00:02:30,483
Come on.

7
00:02:36,689 --> 00:02:37,524
Tim!

8
00:02:45,031 --> 00:02:48,201
(creature roaring)

9
